# Generated audit artifacts: the audit workflow commits these (the human log,
# the ledger, the freshness stamp); they are machine-written, not hand-formatted,
# so prettier must not gate a PR on their style.
audit/*/ledger.json
audit/*/log.md
audit/*/meta.json

# Generated changelogs: changesets writes every package's CHANGELOG.md, so
# like the audit artifacts above they are machine-written, not hand-formatted.
# Keeping them out of the check means a prettier version bump (whose output can
# differ across versions) never gates a PR on changelog churn no human wrote.
**/CHANGELOG.md

